Claudia Nonhlanhla Ndaba (amụrụ na 30 Julaị 1968) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa

Onye otu African National Congress, ọ jere ozi dị ka Onye isi oche nke Kọmitii Portfolio na Women, Youth na People with Disabilities kemgbe 2019 ma bụrụ onye otu National Assembly of South Africa kemgbe 2014
Ọ rụrụ ọrụ dị ka Onye isi oche nke Kọmitii Ad Hoc na Filling of Vacancies na Commission for Gender Equality ugboro abụọ n'oge mbụ ya na ndị omeiwu
Tupu a họpụta ya ka ọ bụrụ onye omeiwu, Ndaba jere ozi dị ka onye otu ndị omeiwu nke Gauteng Provincial Legislature site na 2009 ruo 2014.
Ka ọ na-etolite, ụmụnne nna ya bụ ndị otu ndị agha nke African National Congress, UMkhonto we Sizwe
Ọ debanyere aha na Ann Latsky Nursing College na Johannesburg n'afọ 2002 wee zụọ ka ọ bụrụ onye nọọsụ debanyere akwụkwọ ma mechaa ọzụzụ ya n'afọ 2004
N'afọ 2021, ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Mahadum Pretoria na Bachelor of Public Administration
Mgbe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Ann Latsky Nursing College, ọrụ nọọsụ ya emeghị ka ọ dị ka ọ tụrụ anya ya n'ihi nhọpụta ya dị ka odeakwụkwọ nchịkwa n'ọfịs nke osote minista nke azụmahịa na ụlọ ọrụ.

N'afọ 2009, a họpụtara Ndaba ka ọ bụrụ onye omeiwu Gauteng Provincial Legislature dị ka onye nnọchi anya ANC. A họpụtara ya ka ọ bụrụ osote odeakwụkwọ mpaghara nke African National Congress Women's League na 2012, ọkwá ọ nọrọ ruo n'afọ 2015
Ọ bụkwa onye otu National Executive Committee nke league ụmụ nwanyị.
A họpụtara Ndaba dị ka onye otu National Assembly na ntuli aka 2014 site na ndepụta Gauteng nke ANC. A kpọrọ ya aha na Kọmitii Portfolio na Ahụike

N'afọ 2015, a họpụtara ya ka ọ rụọ ọrụ na Kọmitii Ọrụ Mba nke Njikọ ụmụ nwanyị nke ANC. N'ọnwa Nọvemba 2016, a họpụtara ya ka ọ bụrụ onye isi oche nke Kọmitii Ad Hoc na Filling of Vacancies for Gender Equality. Ndaba ghọrọ onye nnọchi anya Kọmitii Ad Hoc na-ahụ maka ego nke òtù ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị na 21 June 2017.

N'etiti Ọktọba na Nọvemba 2017, ọ bụ onye otu Portfolio Committee on Economic Development, tupu ọ bụrụ onye ọzọ so na kọmitii portfolio. E guzobeghachiri Kọmitii Ad Hoc na-ahụ maka imejuputa oghere na Commission for Gender Equality na 2018 ma họpụta Ndaba ka ọ bụrụ onyeisi oche ọzọ n'enweghị onye na-emegide ya, n'agbanyeghị na ndị otu mmegide na-ahọpụta onye otu ANC Grace Tseke

N'afọ 2019, a họpụtara Ndaba ọzọ na National Assembly, n'oge a dị ka onye na-azọ ọkwa na ndepụta mba ANC. Mgbe ntuli aka ahụ gasịrị, a họpụtara ya ka ọ rụọ ọrụ na Kọmitii Portfolio na Women, Youth and People with Disabilities. A họpụtara Ndaba ka ọ bụrụ onyeisi oche nke kọmitii ahụ, na-anọchi Thandi Memela, onye hapụrụ ndị omeiwu na ntuli aka ahụ.
